      "Loaded 24 images.\n",
      "Scanning Training Set (Extracting parent IDs)...\n",
      "Scanning Validation Set (Extracting parent IDs)...\n",
      "\n",
      "--- TRUE LEAKAGE REPORT ---\n",
      "Unique parent images in Train: 19\n",
